metadata.name: Soulful Symphony
metadata.description:
In the hush of the concert hall,
Where silence reigns supreme,
The symphony of the soul begins
In a wondrous, joyous stream.

Notes that rise like angel's wings
And fall like tears of grace,
They mingle in a harmony
That fills this sacred space.

The melody is sweet and strong,
A balm for hearts that ache,
And every soul is lifted up
By the music that they make.

In every note there's a story told,
A tale of love and pain,
And the symphony of the soul
Brings hope and peace again.

With every chord and every beat,
The music builds and swells,
Until it fills the room with light
And every heart it quells.

And when the final note is played,
The silence is profound,
And every soul is changed and blessed
By the soulful symphony's sound.
